  "texts": [
    "Because false negatives and false positives in medical imaging may have catastrophic effects.",
    "This is one of the reasons why, despite their high performance, standalone decision systems are not widely used.",
    "In this section, we will describe many potential research topics and open concerns for computer vision in medical imaging.",
    "Imaging Modality: Medical imaging modalities are classified according to how images are generated.",
    "In radiology, a modality is a phrase that refers to a certain kind of imaging, such as CT scanning, ultrasound, radiation (x-rays), and MRI."
  ]
}